Integrationstests

	Es gibt mehrere Integrationstest-Module, die dazu dienen, ganze Cumulus4j-Setups automatisiert zu testen.
	Diese Tests werden (zusätzlich zu den Unit-Tests) immer dann automatishc ausgeführt, wenn die Code-Base
	sich ändert. Siehe {{{../surefire-report.html}hier den Test-Bericht}}.

	Additionally to the automatic testing, they provide a way to manually test and analyse certain features.
	For example, Cumulus4j allows for various client implementations which include also
	{{{http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ajax_%28programming%29}Ajax}} clients running in web browsers.
	You can open your browser and try them out (after starting the appropriate servers).

	Here is a list of our integration tests:

	* {{{../org.cumulus4j.integrationtest.gwt/}org.cumulus4j.integrationtest.gwt/index.html}}

	* {{{../org.cumulus4j.integrationtest.webapp/}org.cumulus4j.integrationtest.webapp/index.html}}

	* {{{../org.cumulus4j.integrationtest.withkeyserver/}org.cumulus4j.integrationtest.withkeyserver/index.html}}
